=Description=

"This guide written by Sir John Elvidge sets out 8 steps that governments can take to help communities take more control and make this a success. 
 
The guide is intentionally colourful and accessible and although it is aimed primarily at those in the public sector we hope it will be of interest to anyone working with citizens and communities. 
 
This is the final, report in our Enabling State series. 


